 the valet brought a cloak 
 fool i told you the sable one hey matrena the sable he shouted so that his voice rang far through the rooms 
 a handsome slim and gypsy girl with glittering black eyes and curly hair wearing a red shawl ran out with a sable mantle on her arm 
 here i grudge it take it she said evidently afraid of her master and yet regretful of her cloak 
 dolokhov without answering took the cloak threw it over matrena and wrapped her up in it 
